  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "So, you’re a fresh-faced adventurer who just landed on Victoria Island, huh? Doesn't matter if you're not—it's obvious you're a newbie from a mile away!\n You might’ve done well on Maple Island, but here? Not so fast. If you keep wandering around like that, you’ll be face-down in the dirt before you know it. Get your head in the game!"
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Maybe things’ll change once you hit #blevel 10#k and can advance your job, but I’m not so sure you’ve earned it yet... Fine! I’ll give you some special training to see what you’ve got. How about it?"
      },
      "stop": {
        "_dirName": "stop",
        "_dirType": "sub"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Outside #m10000000#, you’ll find monsters that you’ve never even seen on Maple Island. Take down #r10 #o6#s and 10 #o7#s#k. They’re no pushovers, so don’t forget to grab some potions from the shop!"
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "What’s the matter? Getting cold feet about the training? Hahaha! Don’t worry, you can come back when you’re ready!"
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Well, look who’s back. I honestly thought you might’ve bailed. Alright, let’s see if you actually finished the job."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "You did that flawlessly, huh? Nice! It’s been a while since I’ve seen such an eager newbie adventurer. You’ve got me feeling good! Here, take this special item and put it to good use on your journey!"
        }
      },
      "stop": {
        "_dirName": "stop",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "mob": {
          "_dirName": "mob",
          "_dirType": "sub",
